Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:28.19,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(3300,480)\pos(930,750)\fnDream Han Serif SC W27\c&H743000&\3c&HFAFBFA&\bord6\blur2\fs90\fsp5}小书痴的下克{\fsp0}上\N{\fs30\bord4\fnFZLanTingYuan-DB-GBK\fsp5\blur1}为了成为图书管理员不择手{\fsp0}段\N{\fnDream Han Serif SC W18\fscx90\fsp15\fs70\c&HD79712&\bord5\blur2}领主的养{\fsp0}女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:24.81,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)}在只差一步时跌倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:28.48,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,以为到极限而消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:30.49,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,但我依然坚持前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:34.28,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,不甘心就这样结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:37.24,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,只要闭上双眼想象
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.28,0:01:37.24,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0\t(106,565,\blur2)\t(565,815,\blur0)}只要闭上{\alpha&HFF&}双眼想象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:41.33,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,总能看见你在身旁
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.24,0:01:41.33,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0\t(66,400,\blur2)\t(400,858,\blur0)}总能看见{\alpha&HFF&}你在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:46.29,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,面带我最爱的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.29,0:01:48.59,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:52.47,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,故事还在进行之中
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.59,0:01:52.47,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0\t(2980,3355,\blur3)\t(3355,3772,\blur0)}故事还在进行之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:54.89,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:58.85,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,让我们翻开下一页
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:02.10,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,不用担心我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:05.77,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,只因心中时刻有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:08.90,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,总能听见你的助威
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.65,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,让我变得更加坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:14.07,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,就算觉得坚持不住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:17.83,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,忍不住要流下眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:20.91,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,总能听见你的助威
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.87,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,我一直都感觉良好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.83,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,绝对不会轻言放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:33.01,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H00&\t(5700,6180,\alpha&HC8&)}爱的力量多么神奇
Comment: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ending
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.20,0:21:43.28,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(980,0)}就算身处遥远又未知的星球
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.28,0:21:47.41,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,仰望着头顶的那片陌生的天空
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.41,0:21:51.37,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,就算深爱过的人和许下的诺言
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.37,0:21:54.63,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,还有其他的一切都不在手边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:59.63,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\t(750,1810,\alpha&H00&)\3c&HB5C2BF&\bord6\blur4}我依然记忆犹新
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.63,0:21:59.63,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,我依然记忆犹新
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:02.76,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HB5C2BF&\bord6\blur4}时间之海默默记录着你的一切
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.63,0:22:02.76,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,时间之海默默记录着你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.76,0:22:09.93,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H00&\t(690,1840,\alpha&HFF&)\3c&HB5C2BF&\bord6\blur4}你轻轻推开了沉没在海中的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.76,0:22:09.93,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,你轻轻推开了沉没在海中的
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.93,0:22:12.06,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,那扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:13.77,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1100,0)\3c&HBED6CA&\bord6\blur4}Wanna me Wanna me Wanna me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.06,0:22:13.77,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,Wanna me Wanna me Wanna me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:17.86,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HBED6CA&\bord6\blur4}在别人对我有所认知之前
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.77,0:22:17.86,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,在别人对我有所认知之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:20.15,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HBED6CA&\bord6\blur4}我实际上
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.86,0:22:20.15,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,我实际上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:21.99,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1840)\3c&HBED6CA&\bord6\blur4}Gonna me Gonna me Gonna me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.15,0:22:21.99,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,Gonna me Gonna me Gonna me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.99,0:22:24.95,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,对自己有清楚的认知
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.95,0:22:28.33,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,独自一人也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.33,0:22:30.12,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1810,0)\3c&HACA69C&\bord6\blur4}随着季节更替
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.33,0:22:30.12,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,随着季节更替
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:36.46,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HACA69C&\bord6\blur4}与互相拥抱取暖的某人相遇又离别
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.12,0:22:36.46,EDCN2,,0,0,0,,与互相拥抱取暖的某人相遇又离别
